issue.body:
I think it would be convenient to have public access to LottieComposition properties getters:
```
  Rect getBounds() {
    return bounds;
  }

  long getDuration() {
    return duration;
  }

  long getEndFrame() {
    return endFrame;
  }

  int getFrameRate() {
    return frameRate;
  }

  List<Layer> getLayers() {
    return layers;
  }

  long getStartFrame() {
    return startFrame;
  }

  boolean hasMasks() {
    return hasMasks;
  }

  boolean hasMattes() {
    return hasMattes;
  }

  float getScale() {
    return scale;
  }
```
